## Open Questions

- How many third-year CS students have tried and abandoned at least one tool? My guess after this interview is most of them.
- Is there a way to make a solution that survives Moodle changes without active maintenance?
- Does learned helplessness reverse if a tool actually works for a full semester, or is the trust permanently damaged?

